{"tid":2212713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国民居突發爆炸  一女子從窗口被炸飛出5樓全身赤裸","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T08:02:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"11f5bfe0a2303744c0749fcd48acf1ccaef69f86","tid":2212713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"中國遼寧省大連市旅順一居民樓昨天突發爆炸，巨響後一女子從窗口被炸出5樓。<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，9月21日早5點40分左右，遼寧大連旅順鐵山鹽北路附近一住宅樓5樓一居民家中突然傳來劇烈的爆炸聲，一名女子被炸出窗外後送醫。居民樓前掉下了大片玻璃碎片和窗框碎片，5樓一戶居民家的陽臺和臥室窗戶全被炸飛。<br />\n<br />\n事發現場緊鄰道路，一樓是公建。出事的居民家位於5樓。5樓這戶居民家的外陽臺牆體也在事故中被炸變形。樓下停放的車輛也有遭受殃及的。<br />\n<br />\n據1樓商戶史女士稱，該爆炸疑似天然氣泄漏引發，女子被炸出時一絲不掛，親屬表示女子送醫後身亡。<br />\n<br />\n但官方未通報有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2020-09/1000-1600735006450.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2020-09%2F1000-1600735006450.png&h=7330fea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/424282?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F424282%3Flang%3Db5&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=acc4ea16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/424282?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"f6293c19731be639d44447b582af8b244a38fad7","tid":2212713,"uid":11291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"全身赤裸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5218b2e77e9417259b3a1ad8733b2f76a20ee313","tid":2212713,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2369b242988a831d548be67b5a1eb4125afcd16","tid":2212713,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"中國永遠有你想像唔到既事發生"},{"pid":"d4c7dd9b283de797a41f078c89c5dd8552a79870","tid":2212713,"uid":286897,"like":33,"dislike":1,"sc